        "id": "Q1",
        "Topic": "nth term",
        "subquestion_1": "Finding the first term (a): Determine the value of the first element ($a_1$) given the common difference ($d$) and a specific $n^{th}$ term ($a_n$).",
        "subquestion_2": "Finding the common difference (d): Determine the constant difference ($d$) given the first term ($a_1$) and the value of a specific $n^{th}$ term ($a_n$).",
        "subquestion_3": "Finding the term number (n): Determine the position ($n$) of a given term value ($a_n$) in the sequence, given the first term ($a_1$) and the common difference ($d$)."
